title: Industrial Zine Archive [part2]
description:
This is a complete rip of everything 433RPM has posted to his blog Notes From Underground. An essential library of 80's underground as written by the artists who lived and created it. Most all the links on his blog are still currently active thanks to 433RPM's tireless dedication to re-uploading. This torrent should serve as a backup. 

I had to RAR a bunch of it up because the .torrent file was too big for TPB.
